title: Malaysia Job Vacancies
description: Job Vacancies in Malaysia decreased to 1028770 in the third quarter of 2022 from 1432799 in the second quarter of 2022. Job Vacancies in Malaysia averaged 253134.61  from 1997 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1432799  in the second quarter of 2022 and a record low of 7850  in the first quarter of 2004. This page provides - Malaysia Job Vacancies - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Malaysia
